data.description: Incredible East Memphis Prime location! New Roof 6/2020! Adjacent to Sea Isle Park! Refinished Hardwood Floors, New paint throughout, Updated Kitchen w/ new SS appliances, granite, new tile floors!  Updated Master bath with furniture piece vantiy. Den Fireplace with floor to ceiling stone. Newer HVAC. Storage building and carport storage room! This is just a gem and won't last long. Adjacent to Sea Isle Park ..... so walkable!
